column3: “I just brought this lovely strain home in Shatter form. Nug Run by Newt Brothers. Coming in at 75.5% THCA this shatter is damn tasty!!! Has a slight sweet flavor can’t quite pinpoint it. So far it doesn’t ring as banana but I will continue to smoke on it. It’s a pretty quick hitter. Definitely a cerebral feeling that melts into the rest of your body very slowly. “Dank shit amazing smooth with a subtly heavy high”
